            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8d3453b0-852d-43b3-a09c-2e284291c8fe">
                Mr. Clement Davies (Montgomery)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8d3453b0-852d-43b3-a09c-2e284291c8fe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
