        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I beg to move that you, Sir, follow the course you did in the case of the first Motion, and have this Resolution recorded as having been agreed to <em>nemine contradicente.</em></p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
